      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/europe-faces-diesel-deluge-as-giant-supertankers-bring-fuel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大量柴油正涌入欧洲，原本用于运输原油的巨型油轮改道从数千英里外的中东卸下大量精炼燃料。]]></description>
